  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1701979171\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1701979171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1701979171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your deduction skills and your cinema knowledge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/e02994c3ce587ea58233a42971f86b42.avif?t=1701979171\" width=600 height=102 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock new levels with hits</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/6790514df9ac8d214afb7ad9794689e1.avif?t=1701979171\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each level has a category</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/6cc7f518eb9d656ea5949ac1c45ec523.poster.avif?t=1701979171\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/6cc7f518eb9d656ea5949ac1c45ec523.webm?t=1701979171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/6cc7f518eb9d656ea5949ac1c45ec523.mp4?t=1701979171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some filmemojis are hard to guess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582950/extras/7a7d5d1e8ad34bc9c7635a3b98bd7fa4.avif?t=1701979171\" width=600 height=102 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 200 handcrafted filmemojis to guess.<br></li><li> 40 levels with 5 filmemoji.<br></li><li> Each level belongs to one of the following categories: classic, horror, action, comedy, thriller, romance, drama, adventure, science fiction, animation, western, fantasy, biography, musical, cult, miscellaneous and hard.<br></li><li> It's pretty hard to guess alone all filmemojis.<br></li><li> Has hidden achievments...</li></ul>",
